## Current Architecture (Updated)

### Layer Stack

```
┌─────────────────────────────────────────┐
│   HTTP/Hertz Layer                       │
│   - Routes                               │
│   - Request parsing                      │
└─────────────────────────────────────────┘
                  ↓
┌─────────────────────────────────────────┐
│   Middleware Chain                       │
│   ✅ Request ID                          │
│   ✅ Observability (logging)             │
│   ✅ Schema Validation (request)         │
│   📋 Authentication (JWT) - NEW          │
│   ✅ Authorization (OPA)                 │
│   📋 Policy Loader (.rego) - NEW         │
│   ✅ Recovery, CORS, Timeout             │
└─────────────────────────────────────────┘
                  ↓
┌─────────────────────────────────────────┐
│   Application/Handler Layer              │
│   ✅ Directory handlers                  │
│   📋 Auth handlers - NEW                 │
│   📋 Admin handlers (users/groups) - NEW │
│   ⏳ File handlers (with validation)     │
│   - Request/response mapping             │
│   - Error handling                       │
└─────────────────────────────────────────┘
                  ↓
┌─────────────────────────────────────────┐
│   Domain/Business Logic Layer            │
│   ✅ DirectoryService                    │
│   ✅ ContentValidator                    │
│   📋 SchemaLoader (with caching) - NEW   │
│   📋 PolicyLoader (with caching) - NEW   │
│   📋 Special file helpers - NEW          │
│   ⏳ FileService (with validation)       │
│   - Pure business rules                  │
│   - Zero infrastructure deps             │
└─────────────────────────────────────────┘
                  ↓
┌─────────────────────────────────────────┐
│   Repository Layer                       │
│   ✅ DirectoryRepository                 │
│   ✅ FileRepository                      │
│   ✅ EventRepository                     │
│   📋 UserRepository - NEW                │
│   📋 GroupRepository - NEW               │
│   ✅ Unit of Work                        │
└─────────────────────────────────────────┘
                  ↓
┌─────────────────────────────────────────┐
│   Infrastructure                         │
│   ✅ GORM implementations                │
│   ✅ Models (Directory, File, etc.)      │
│   📋 Models (User, Group) - NEW          │
│   ✅ Database connection                 │
│   📋 JWT token utilities - NEW           │
│   📋 Password hashing - NEW              │
└─────────────────────────────────────────┘
